# ── Course workspaces (personal study data) ──────────────────
# courses/ contains session logs, quiz records, source materials,
# and progress data. This is private and must not be published
# to the public template repo.
#
# Students who want to track their own progress in a private fork
# can remove this line from their personal copy of .gitignore.
courses/

# ── Root-level files left over from /init-coach test runs ────
# These should not exist in the template repo. Delete them with:
#   rm memory.md progress.md cheatsheet.md misses.md cases.md \
#      SOURCES.md DIAGNOSTIC.md CALIBRATION.md
# The root CLAUDE.md is the static dispatcher — it IS committed.
memory.md
progress.md
cheatsheet.md
misses.md
cases.md
SOURCES.md
DIAGNOSTIC.md
CALIBRATION.md

